## Grounding Facts (verified 2026-06-24)

- `apps/coordinator-api/src/app/` — 485 .py files, 34 bounded contexts under `contexts/` (each with `domain/`, `routers/`, `services/`, `storage/` subpackages). Only `contexts/agent_identity/` and `contexts/marketplace/` are fully populated; most others have empty `domain/` stubs.
- `apps/coordinator-api/src/app/domain/` — 25 flat domain model files (6,859 lines) still the live import target. 38 cross-context imports reach into it from 10 contexts.
- `apps/agent-coordinator/` — separate microservice, 61 .py files, flat layout. 103 endpoints across 15 routers. 12 of 15 routers use `@rate_limit`.
- **Rate limiter is NOT a no-op** — `aitbc/rate_limiting.py` is enabled by default (`AITBC_ENABLE_RATE_LIMITING=true`), enforces via `RateLimiter`, returns 429 on exceed. Fixed in commits `71cec61bf` + `c08e85b03`.
- **JWT libraries**: both services now use `PyJWT` 2.13.0 only. `python-jose` removed from deps.

